{"tid":795934,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[甲蟲王者]夜晚個廳成日發現呢隻蟲 究竟咩黎？","createTime":"2018-08-27T11:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T23:26:16.000Z","uid":13653,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc29af8b5bff2f23ee8fdfb2e8dc4006da01a45c","tid":795934,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"夜晚十二後，屋企熄晒燈，得我同隻兔係廳談心<br />\n成日會發現一兩隻呢啲細粒蟲行黎行去<br />\n但唔知係咪曱甴，要趕絕佢地要點搞？<br />\n<br />\n想殺佢地要先隱藏殺氣，趁佢唔為意一野致命<br />\n否則佢會用極高移速逃走，係極高速！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為免嚇親怕蟲既巴絲，特意提醒下面有圖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/192854_338c5e7447cf3fcc456a34da10c81fe0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F192854_338c5e7447cf3fcc456a34da10c81fe0.png&h=891a4a47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16422008421abb8dde3b76d96bc3fcd882fc18b1","tid":795934,"uid":69794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"甲由皇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab1efa125412c2def7c6ea28215e549ea298130","tid":795934,"uid":10635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"德國蟑螂"},{"pid":"82c6c2ac9c6c729437df8dd928e03871407eacca","tid":795934,"uid":61259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"無咩事 小強姐"},{"pid":"58371801d9f5b1ac53e755148aeb5de86cf51cca","tid":795934,"uid":109173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"樓豬邊樹鄉下?甲由都未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c1590b5cbdaaa3938a2591e234694eb17d6b82","tid":795934,"uid":169992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"棕帶蟑螂